{"tid":2437780,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"「大陸打壓荒謬 無辜農民受害」 港人撐台 672箱鳳梨五小時掃光","createTime":"2021-03-08T05:44:05.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-08T06:08:24.000Z","uid":25558,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"9e8df8e03eac44d1f3e2eddcf2c7704c1583eb18","tid":2437780,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T05:44:05.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210308/EQCNBTM4HVCRNOJIJLJJOLLF3M/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210308%2FEQCNBTM4HVCRNOJIJLJJOLLF3M%2F&d=7kduTEFmP9pIRK3EkT058rtFVp6nBI01qSlVibQweWg%3D&h=bd4bf9e9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210308%2FEQCNBTM4HVCRNOJIJLJJOLLF3M%2F&h=61bca63a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210308/EQCNBTM4HVCRNOJIJLJJOLLF3M/</a><br />\n<br />\n「大陸打壓荒謬 無辜農民受害」<br />\n港人撐台 672箱鳳梨五小時掃光<br />\n<br />\n【《蘋果》直擊】<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：廣東店舖有售 民眾屈撐台獨<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】大陸封殺台灣鳳梨（港稱菠蘿），反成為最佳宣傳大使。大陸暫停進口鳳梨禁令本月1日起生效，澳門疑似追隨大陸，翌日亦停止進口。鳳梨品質優良卻慘被打壓，港人風雨同舟， 出現「撐台灣，買鳳梨」熱潮。有本港果商早前從台購入一貨櫃逾600箱鳳梨，短短五小時便全數售出，負責人向本報表示希望熱潮過後，港人仍會繼續支持台灣果農，繼續撐台。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/prpyxi22k95oPz8y61Ns5iCvTnQ=/510x765/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/OI7YXWHNOVC63PFGILTCOAKJDU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fprpyxi22k95oPz8y61Ns5iCvTnQ%3D%2F510x765%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FOI7YXWHNOVC63PFGILTCOAKJDU.jpg&h=da057ad5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■巴打鮮菓負責人梁東麒昨點收鳳梨，冀港人可持續支持台灣果農。<br />\n<br />\n近日本港不少網上購物平台開設台灣鳳梨訂購服務，標榜產地直送，例如教協提供預購「台農17號金鑽鳳梨」，。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/3EOBlRaB-zhsgCMQM-b_B5DsYFY=/510x339/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/DR5XVBYJARFDPIYNFGDLLWHONY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F3EOBlRaB-zhsgCMQM-b_B5DsYFY%3D%2F510x339%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FDR5XVBYJARFDPIYNFGDLLWHONY.jpg&h=bff9dd33&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■巴打鮮菓店面昨堆滿台灣鳳梨，顧客紛紛前來取貨。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n店東冀熱潮後持續支持<br />\n<br />\n網上專營水果速遞的「巴打鮮菓」則率先到貨，本報昨日直擊拆櫃過程，。。。。。。。。。，短短五小時就全被掃清，速度之快出乎意料，大部份顧客都開宗名義撐台，「大陸今次拒絕接受台灣鳳梨，令全世界好多地方都想支持台灣」，。。。。。。。。，「呢啲支持應該係長期持續會更好」。<br />\n<br />\n黃大仙大成街林記水果負責人。。。。。。。。，「自禁運新聞後，大家都覺得呢個決定係別有用心，有針對性」。<br />\n<br />\n林指現時抵港的鳳梨仍未達最佳狀態，有台灣果農向他明言，4月鳳梨當造，產量是「山洪暴發」級數，味道亦會更好，。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n鳳梨昨抵港，港人施先生即到水果店取貨，他表示。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/W5H7IKAfYMJX2262dJnOs1pHwP0=/510x340/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/SYQEW5SBRVG4RHQZZGZI6PVLW4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FW5H7IKAfYMJX2262dJnOs1pHwP0%3D%2F510x340%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FSYQEW5SBRVG4RHQZZGZI6PVLW4.jpg&h=ceff1e23&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■買家施先生昨即場試食鳳梨，大讚口感與味道俱有特色。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n買家：食唔晒分畀朋友<br />\n<br />\n另一前來取貨的陳小姐買了一箱鳳梨，她坦言除了支持入口鳳梨的水果店，同時亦以行動撐台，。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n大陸當局自上月底稱「驗出介殼蟲」，宣佈本月1日起禁止台灣鳳梨進口，香港親中媒體中評社日前指澳門已跟緊北京腳步，僅香港仍維持進口鳳梨。。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/HwDiU9O4zreAJjEUZuGiApXlpiA=/510x560/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/V3FJLBRVKFE5BL7B6DQGCTUMIQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FHwDiU9O4zreAJjEUZuGiApXlpiA%3D%2F510x560%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FV3FJLBRVKFE5BL7B6DQGCTUMIQ.jpg&h=35670dc3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0f8596190050149ca7d0c8079d2cbafb444fb35f","tid":2437780,"uid":353635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T06:06:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />買買買"},{"pid":"f0c3bc655ea143e58939dc8758fd16ee8c357e53","tid":2437780,"uid":171506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T06:06:39.000Z","msg":"食得好"},{"pid":"1e7cb9b67fcf99c3682e32dc16acadaab8a531c4","tid":2437780,"uid":77196,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T06:08:24.000Z","msg":"BAN親都係熱門貨，做鄰國人慘到就黎食屎 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}